com.abdulrhmanil.wallhavenwallpapers

Class DisplayUtil.ThumbRes

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.abdulrhmanil.wallhavenwallpapers.DisplayUtil.ThumbRes
  • Enclosing class:
    DisplayUtil

    public static class DisplayUtil.ThumbRes
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that able to calculate and determine : 1 - the number of thumb photos in one line. 2 - the width of the thumb photo. 3 - the height of the thumb photo. With keeping the photo scaled with her the original dimensions, this class do the calculation and keep the needed numbers in 3 public Fields : 1 - widthPx, 2 - heightPx, 3 - numOfCols .
